briefTitle: Safety Study of GSK Biologicals' Human Papillomavirus Vaccine in 580299/008 Subjects From Canada or the US
officialTitle: Safety Study of GSK Biologicals' Human Papillomavirus Vaccine (GSK580299) in Female American and Canadian Subjects Who Had Received Control Vaccine in Study 580299/008
summary: This phase 3b study is designed to assess the safety of GlaxoSmithKline Biological's HPV vaccine GSK580299 in female subjects who took part in study 580299/008 and received the control vaccine (Hepatitis A vaccine).

primaryOutcome.measure: Number of Subjects With Any, Grade 3 and Related Serious Adverse Events (SAEs)
